Fadwa Sidi Madane (amụrụ na 20 Nọvemba na afọ 1994) bụ onye Morocco na-agba ọsọ n'etiti. O sonyere na ihe omume steeplechase nke mita 3000 na afo 2015 World Championships in Athletics na Beijing, China.
N'afọ 2017, o sonyere na asọmpi steeplechase nke ụmụ nwanyị 3000 mita na afọ 2017 World Championships in Athletics nke emere na London, United Kingdom. Ọ gara n'ihu ịsọ mpi na nke ikpeazụ.
